kelmore5.java.data.structures.queue

Class Queue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • kelmore5.java.data.structures.queue.Queue<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Generic type of the queue

    public abstract class Queue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
     This abstract class provides the structure of a Queue. A queue is a first in, first out (FIFO) structure.
 I.e. The first element added to the stack is the first element to be removed/seen through pop/peek

 For original work, see Queue
    Date:
    Fall 2012
